{"tid":1182323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想買Doulton濾水器嘅巴絲打入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-02T06:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T06:30:02.000Z","uid":3694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9112d3eae57a65c66da96c955399649ba2026793","tid":1182323,"uid":3694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"事緣係咁嘅，我最近就喺一田嘅Doulton專櫃到買咗個濾水器，叫Townton  T9-CS。<br />\n咁當我去買嘅時候個sales就同我講Townton 同Fairey一樣由英國Fairey所出嘅，只係光面不鏽鋼同磨砂面嘅分別。<br />\n但係當我返到屋企上網再睇一睇啲產品資料嘅時候發現乜鳩Townton 只係一個香港Doulton代理有賣嘅支那貨，得個濾芯係用返英國貨。<br />\n<br />\n為此我已經初步向海關作出咨詢，得到嘅答覆係呢個絕對係一個誤導性嘅商品說明，希望各位買濾水器嘅時候記得睇清楚。唔好因爲喺大舖同代理買就掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n支那Townton<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YW4znvt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYW4znvt.png&h=baa8afc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcfnwoP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcfnwoP.png&h=ebde0fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國Fairey Doulton<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zX1MXG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zX1MXG.png&h=d5f89019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvYwpKm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvYwpKm.png&h=82925ec7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b4d7a323aff1f3b441ed026cd6c097368258568","tid":1182323,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"呢個好似以前已經有post講過<br />\n咁之後有無採取乜嘢行動？"},{"pid":"7ce8c1d9394ece2878b23f2f6f32fd8a3ec907ad","tid":1182323,"uid":3694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b4d7a323aff1f3b441ed026cd6c097368258568","tid":1182323,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"呢個好似以前已經有post講過<br />\n咁之後有無採取乜嘢行動？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"而家準備去返一田同佢退貨，如果唔肯嘅話就會正式向海關立案投訴"},{"pid":"fcbdde48872765040e2f3cc619c8f30482b9